@startuml component_architecture
!theme plain

title UIM Document Management Service — Component Architecture

actor "End User\n(Browser / Client)" as User
actor "Admin / Operator" as Admin

node "Document Management Service Runtime" {
    component "DocumentManagementServer\n(vibe.d REST API)" as Api
    component "DocumentManagementService\n(Business Logic)" as Domain
    component "EncryptionManager\n(AES-256 / XOR-SHA256)" as Crypto
    component "RepositoryRegistry\n(Connector Manager)" as Registry
    database "DocumentManagementStore\n(In-Memory Documents,\nFolders, Versions)" as Store
}

cloud "External CMIS Repository\n(On-Premise / Cloud)" as ExtRepo

User --> Api : REST API calls\n(CRUD, View, Download)
Admin --> Api : Repository mgmt,\nEncryption config
Api --> Domain : route + validate
Domain --> Crypto : encrypt / decrypt content
Domain --> Registry : connect / list repos
Domain --> Store : persist / read / move / copy
Registry --> ExtRepo : CMIS AtomPub binding

note right of Domain
  Features:
  - File & Folder CRUD
  - Breadcrumb navigation
  - Move & Copy operations
  - Document versioning
  - Check-out / Check-in workflow
  - Metadata management
  - Built-in PDF/Image viewer
  - Sorting / personalization
  - Encryption at rest
  - CMIS repository support
end note

@enduml
